These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, german, mexican
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, writing, board-games, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##8
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the brazilian##1
3. the chinese is on the left or right of the german##3
4. the mexican is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
5. the mexican is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the chinese##5
7. the chinese is somewhere between the brazilian and the person who's hobby is writing##7
8. the chinese and the person who's hobby is skydiving have the same parity positions##9
9. the german and the person who's hobby is camping have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | brazilian | chinese | german     | mexican |
| Pet           | board-games   | skydiving     | writing | camping  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, cola, tea
City: hamburg, rome, liverpool, miami
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person traveling to miami and the person drinking coffee have the same parity positions##9
3. the person traveling to rome is not to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##8
4. the person traveling to hamburg is not to the right of the person drinking tea##8
5. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere to the left of the person drinking almond-milk##5
6. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to rome##5
7. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5
8. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | tea     | cola    | almond-milk | coffee    |
| Hobby      | hamburg | rome | liverpool      | miami |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, basketball, biathlon, rowing
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, avocado, mango, pumpkin
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the left of the person eating mango##5
2. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
7. the person eating artichoke is not to the left of the person eating avocado##8
8. the person who's sport is basketball and the person eating avocado have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | basketball    | biathlon   | climbing    | rowing  |
| Food       | avocado | pumpkin | artichoke | mango |

