.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, dressmaker, security-guard, software-developer
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, pakistani, turkish, indonesian
1. the italian is the dressmaker##1
2. the pakistani is on the right of the turkish##1
3. the pakistani is somewhere to the left of the dressmaker##5
4. the indonesian is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
5. the pakistani is on the left of the coach##1
6. the software-developer and the indonesian have the same parity positions##9
7. the security-guard is on the left or right of the coach##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | software-developer | security-guard | coach  | dressmaker |
| Music-Genre   | turkish             | pakistani          | indonesian | italian    |

