.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, may, july, september
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, hedgehog, pony
1. the person who's birthday is in july is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
2. the owner of the cat and the person who's birthday is in december have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the dog and the person who's birthday is in may have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
5. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the person who's birthday is in may is not the owner of the dog##6
7. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
8. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
9. the owner of the pony is not the person who's birthday is in september##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | december | july | september  | may |
| Pet           | dog   | cat     | hedgehog | pony      |

