.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, car, quad-bike, trike
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, indian, thai
1. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
3. the indian is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5
4. the american and the person driving the quad-bike have the same parity positions##9
5. the person driving the trike and the american have different parity positions##9
6. the indian is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8
7. the thai is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
8. the person driving the car is not to the right of the thai##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | car | scooter | quad-bike | trike |
| Nationality   | thai        | indian    | american   | brazilian |

