.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-8::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, hip-hop, punk, salsa
4 different games are played: go, billiard, snooker, scrabble
1. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5
2. the person playing scrabble is between the person playing billiard and the person playing snooker##2
3. the person playing scrabble and the fan salsa have different parity positions##9
4. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing go##1
5. the fan salsa is not to the right of the fan punk##8
6. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the fan punk##5
7. the fan salsa is somewhere to the right of the fan funk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | hip-hop | salsa         | punk     |
| Sport         | billiard | scrabble  | snooker | go |

