3. the fan indie is on the right of the fan ambient##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is not the fan metal##6
6. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking and the fan indie have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | woodworking | gardening | filmmaking | singing |
| Pet     | r&b     | ambient     | indie     | metal    |

