4 different pets are kept: ferret, snake, bird, horse
1. the person eating peach and the owner of the horse have the same parity positions##9
2. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the person eating peach##8
3. the person eating mango is somewhere between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the horse##7
4. the owner of the horse is somewhere between the owner of the bird and the person eating mango##7
5. the owner of the snake is not the person eating tomato##6
6. the person eating peach is on the right of the person eating mango##1
7. the person eating potato is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | tomato | mango | peach | potato  |
| Music-Genre   | ferret    | snake | horse | bird |

