.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, sprite, tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, soccer, baseball
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is not the person drinking tea##6
2. the person drinking tea is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
7. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
8. the person who's sport is biathlon and the person drinking almond-milk have the same parity positions##9
9. the person who's sport is soccer and the person drinking sprite have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | tea   | fanta  | sprite  | almond-milk |
| Movie-Genre   | rugby | soccer | baseball | biathlon      |

