.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-17::.
House: cape-cod, gothic-revival, farmhouse, futuristic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, jazz, r&b, soul
 1. the gothic-revival house and the fan r&b have the same parity positions##9
 2. the farmhouse house is not to the right of the gothic-revival house##8
 3. the fan blues is somewhere between the gothic-revival house and the cape-cod house##7
 4. the fan r&b is somewhere to the left of the farmhouse house##5
 5. the farmhouse house is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan r&b is not to the left of the futuristic house##8
 7. the futuristic house and the fan jazz have the same parity positions##9
 8. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the fan soul##3
 9. the fan soul is in an odd position##4
10. the futuristic house is not to the right of the fan blues##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage      | cape-cod  | futuristic | farmhouse  | gothic-revival |
| Music-Genre   | soul | r&b     | blues | jazz     |

