.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, juice, water
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, biathlon, basketball, handball
 1. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
 2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is not to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##8
 4. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's sport is surfing is not the person drinking cola##6
 6. the person drinking water is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
 7. the person drinking water and the person who's sport is biathlon have the same parity positions##9
 8. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
 9. the person drinking water is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
10. the person drinking cola and the person who's sport is biathlon have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | cola    | juice        | water   | coffee      |
| Hobby      | handball | basketball | biathlon | surfing |

 